Package: cooccur
Title: Co-Occurrence Networks from Any Data Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build co-occurrence networks from delimited fields, long/bipartite
    tables, binary matrices, wide sequences, or plain lists. Returns tidy
    edge data frames with eight similarity measures (Jaccard, cosine,
    association strength, etc.) and optional scaling. Convert results to
    igraph, cograph, Nestimate, or tidygraph objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
